Step 1: Start
Step 2: Store Input Address in DPTR
Step 3: Store 04 in R0
Step 4: Store Value of DPTR in Accumulator
Step 5: Push DPTR Value to Stack
Step 6: Store FFC0 in DPTR
Step 7: Produce Delay
Step 8: Move Accumulator Value to DPTR
Step 9: Pop Values into DPTR
Step 10: Increment DPTR
Step 11: Decrement R0 and Go to Step 4
Step 12: Go to Step 2
Step 13: Stop